                                <td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td><a href="viewtopic.php?p=41390&amp;sid=bde588f6daa68252bb3152ec6b69fa45#41390"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Thu May 06, 2004 3:12 pm<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: New expansion. thoughts and suggestions.</span></td>
                                <td align="right" valign="top" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=41390&amp;sid=bde588f6daa68252bb3152ec6b69fa45"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>    </td></tr></table></td>
